<body>

<h1>🛣 PROJECT ROADMAP: INFINITY FINANCE (LOANBRICK)</h1>
<p style="text-align:center;"><em>Strategic phases for system deployment, optimization, and scaling.</em></p>

<h2>📅 Phase 1: Production Onboarding & Migration</h2>
<p><strong>Focus:</strong> Data Accuracy & Live Transaction Baseline | <strong>Timeline:</strong> Week 1 (Immediate)</p>
<ul class="bullet-list">
    <li><strong>Weekly Borrower Migration:</strong> Bulk import of all active weekly borrower profiles with encrypted PII and onboarding of current loan balances.</li>
    <li><strong>Financial Reconciliation:</strong> Validation of migrated portfolio totals and verification of PAR (Portfolio At Risk) accuracy.</li>
    <li><strong>Field Staff Training:</strong> Collector walkthroughs for offline sync and remittance workflows.</li>
</ul>

<h2>📊 Phase 2: Advanced Reporting & Analytics</h2>
<p><strong>Focus:</strong> Evaluation Tools & Operational Insights | <strong>Timeline:</strong> Week 2 - 3</p>
<ul class="bullet-list">
    <li><strong>Borrower Renewal Evaluation:</strong> New reporting module to analyze repayment history and provide "Approved/Rejected" recommendations.</li>
    <li><strong>Financial Cash Flow Reporting:</strong> Dynamic Cash Flow statement tracking operational inflows vs. lending outflows.</li>
    <li><strong>Printing & Documentation:</strong> Bulk generation of <strong>Loan Vouchers</strong> for new and renewed loans.</li>
</ul>

<h2>📲 Phase 3: Engagement & Scaling</h2>
<p><strong>Focus:</strong> Automated Communication & Multi-Branch Support | <strong>Timeline:</strong> Month 1 - 2</p>
<ul class="bullet-list">
    <li><strong>SMS Gateway Integration:</strong> Automated payment reminders and instant digital receipts for borrowers via SMS.</li>
    <li><strong>Multi-Branch Architecture:</strong> Hierarchical setup to support multiple branch locations and centralized head-office reporting.</li>
    <li><strong>Live Collector Tracking (GPS):</strong> Real-time map view of collector locations and route optimization.</li>
</ul>

<h2>🛡 Phase 4: Long-term Optimization</h2>
<p><strong>Focus:</strong> Governance & AI Insights | <strong>Timeline:</strong> Month 3+</p>
<ul class="bullet-list">
    <li><strong>Comprehensive Audit Logs:</strong> Immutable history of all data transactions for regulatory compliance and internal audit.</li>
    <li><strong>Credit Scoring Engine:</strong> Behavioral credit scoring based on observed repayment patterns over time.</li>
    <li><strong>Automated Savings Dividends:</strong> Systematic calculation of interest for borrower capital savings accounts.</li>
</ul>

<br><br>

